<item>
            <title>[LU-4762] lctl set_param should return error when the value of the parameter is null</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-4762</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;This problem was found by &lt;a href=&quot;https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-4748&quot; title=&quot;sanity test 116b: error: set_param: /proc/{fs,sys}/{lnet,lustre}/17%: Found no match&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;LU-4748&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;LU-4748&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt; when MDSCOUNT=2&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;preformatted panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;preformattedContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre&gt;#lctl set_param lov.*mdtlov*.qos_threshold_rr=17% 17%
lov.lustre-MDT0000-mdtlov.qos_threshold_rr=17%
lov.lustre-MDT0001-mdtlov.qos_threshold_rr=17%
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Also, it&apos;s easy to be found by running the following commands:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;preformatted panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;preformattedContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre&gt;#lctl set_param debug_mb
#lctl set_param fail_loc=
fail_loc=
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;I will push a patch later.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
